# Project Skills

This repo keeps Cursor Agent Skills in `skills/` at the repository root.

When a task matches a skill's description, or the user mentions a skill by name:

1. Look for a matching folder under `skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md`.
2. Read that `SKILL.md` (and linked files in the same folder) before acting.
3. Follow the skill's instructions precisely.

Do not invent skill behavior when a matching skill file exists — read it first.

To add skills, see `skills/README.md`.
